snippet.title: Hitman - Blood Money - L.A. Edition (J2ME)
snippet.description:
http://www.projectnext.de/
Title: Hitman - Blood Money - L.A. Edition
By: Eidos
Phone: Nokia S60

Game INFO
Hitman Bloodmoney LA - Money Talks. Silence Pays. Prepare to Make a Killing. Enter the Dark underworld of organised crime as Agent 47, the ruthlessly efficient and professional Hitman. Your mission and objectives are issued by the ever present mission controller, DIANA. Can you achieve your objectives and dispatch your targets while remaining undetected? 

For additional information visit: http://www.projectnext.de/thread.php?threadid=2222
